name: Elephant
description:
2015 felt like the beginning of something big, grand! Interestingly, the world resonated with this feeling and gave me the opportunity to write almost every day. Now I see the continuation of this movement, so it's just beginning again!

Artwork created by Maksym Denysenko in 2015, 70x50cm, spray paint on canvas, photo by Sergey Nozhevnikov using ultraviolet, JPG, 2958x2097 pix, 1.5 Mb.
